{"tid":9180,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【手機恐怖GAME】你執到一部陌生既電話 .....","createTime":"2016-11-28T14:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T15:25:03.000Z","uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00b3de0d79a2551c65d487abaf79bdc50a9c083e","tid":9180,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"恐怖故事，由你撿到一部陌生人的電話開始．．．<br />\n<br />\n你撿到一部屬於某位陌生人的手提電話，電話簿裡面的通訊記錄、Whatsapp短訊、相片庫均被刪去，電話幾乎成為空殼。此時電話裡面的人工智能「SIRI」竟主動跟你溝通，指電話的物主失蹤多時並似乎身陷某種危險，SIRI打算逐步恢復電話功能與還原被刪訊息，讓你可以幫它找出「主人」下落．．．《Sara Is Missing》就是一款這樣的遊戲，亦是一款最值得期待的手機恐怖遊戲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/220915_84ef30a06b5e232f5ce156b2ef3493b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F220915_84ef30a06b5e232f5ce156b2ef3493b2.jpg&h=12144272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然形式不同，但《Sara Is Missiing》（下稱SIM）的概念其實與年前另一風評極佳之作《Her Story》十分相近。《SIM》的遊戲畫面就跟一般手機介面無異，玩家透過翻查電郵、短訊通話來尋找「SARA」下落，抽絲剝繭找出SARA身陷險境的原因，期間IRIS（其實電話的人工智能叫IRIS，不是SIRI）只會提供少量協助，更重要的是IRIS似乎不是個可以完全信任的對象．．．<br />\n<br />\nwsUNHD▲遊戲畫面就有如大家的電話介面。一旦進入遊戲，你手上的再也不是屬於你的電話，而是主角SARA的失物<br />\n<br />\nhVZCFn▲聯絡人資料、短訊內容、電郵，僅存在電話裡面的資料是引導你找出SARA的關鍵<br />\n<br />\n既然《SIM》是恐怖遊戲，大家很容易會聯想起JUMPSCARE－－突如其來的恐怖畫面與尖叫聲，任誰都會被嚇到，也是最廉價的恐怖來源。《SIM》帶出的「恐怖」並非這一種，而是透過氣氛與展示方式將玩家帶入遊戲世界，雖然遊戲還是會有恐怖的畫面與音效（大部份涉及暗網（Deep Web）），但真正令玩家陷入恐慌的還是逐步揭開事件真相的緊張氣氛，與及由獨特操作帶來的投入感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/220935_40fc698069baf8bd1d76a64f6ba86c74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F220935_40fc698069baf8bd1d76a64f6ba86c74.jpg&h=a6fe511e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nmaxresdefault▲遊戲還是有少量驚嚇畫面與音效，但份量有限，並非遊戲最大恐怖感來源<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://mtgamer.com/%E3%80%90%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%81%90%E6%80%96game%E3%80%91%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BD%A0%E6%92%BF%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E9%99%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmtgamer.com%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596game%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B%25EF%25BC%258C%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%2592%25BF%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2599%258C%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%2F&d=JGgYy0LqdrBMYXb44KbCrsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=54a11e7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mtgamer.com/%E3%80%90%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%81%90%E6%80%96game%E3%80%91%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BD%A0%E6%92%BF%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E9%99%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84/</a>"},{"pid":"f5ba79b28f830f4b71f738f00eccf626212a3a6a","tid":9180,"uid":13047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"好似幾正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d9c4e76878c1ea3c932bd4a4fd9d6adfe0e1a3","tid":9180,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"好想download 黎玩 但我IOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed2d885a1947a09c8aae856bcc4cd3cd844ca59","tid":9180,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}